OL,3,C'It's soul-destroying:' Mum of
OL,4,Cautistic twins quoted #1k per week for
OL,5,Cchildcare
OL,7,FA mother of twins who are autistic
OL,8,Fsays it is a "constant battle" to try
OL,9,Fand access inclusive childcare, being
OL,10,Fquoted #1,000 for a week's one-to-one
OL,11,Fprivate childcare.
OL,13,FBetsan Gower Gallagher says she is
OL,14,F"scared for the future" as she
OL,15,Fstruggles to find appropriate and
OL,16,Faffordable support for her seven-year-
OL,17,Fold twins Brielle and Bowann, who both
OL,18,Fhave additional learning needs.
