OL,3,C'It's soul-destroying:' Mum of
OL,4,Cautistic twins quoted #1k per week for
OL,5,Cchildcare
OL,7,FIt comes days after after a damning
OL,8,FSenedd report found that a significant
OL,9,Fnumber of children and young people's
OL,10,Fright to an education is being denied
OL,11,Fthroughout Wales, while inclusive
OL,12,Fchildcare is not accessible to all.
OL,14,FWhile Betsan's twins now attend a
OL,15,Fschool which is "perfect" for them,
OL,16,Fshe says childcare continues to be a
OL,17,Fmajor issue.
