OL,3,C'It's soul-destroying:' Mum of
OL,4,Cautistic twins quoted #1k per week for
OL,5,Cchildcare
OL,7,FBetsan, from the Swansea Valley, said:
OL,8,F"It's difficult to have one disabled
OL,9,Fchild, and I have two high-needs
OL,10,Fdisabled children.
OL,12,F"I just feel like I've been punished
OL,13,Fbecause I've got disabled children,
OL,14,Fand I feel like my children are being
OL,15,Fpunished. They didn't choose to be
OL,16,Fdisabled.
OL,18,F"I'm not asking for money, but I'm
OL,19,Fcertainly asking for some kind of set-
OL,20,Fup that can help and support children
OL,21,Flike mine."
