OL,3,C'It's soul-destroying:' Mum of
OL,4,Cautistic twins quoted #1k per week for
OL,5,Cchildcare
OL,7,FShe said her daughters don't get the
OL,8,Fsame opportunities as other children
OL,9,Fto take part in activities out of
OL,10,Fschool hours.
OL,12,F"The children don't have access to
OL,13,Fbreakfast clubs and after school
OL,14,Fclubs, and I think there's a lot of
OL,15,Fpeople who are totally and utterly
OL,16,Funaware of that," she said.
OL,18,FBetsan said she feels compelled to
OL,19,Fhelp other parents of children with
OL,20,Fadditional learning needs by speaking
OL,21,Fout about the challenges they face.
