OL,3,C'It's soul-destroying:' Mum of
OL,4,Cautistic twins quoted #1k per week for
OL,5,Cchildcare
OL,7,FShe said: "My passion, my anger and my
OL,8,Ffears are propelling me to be vocal
OL,9,Fabout this and to fight.
OL,11,F"People are so unaware of the
OL,12,Fstruggles - it's exhausting and hard
OL,13,Fwork, the paperwork is ridiculous, the
OL,14,Fphone calls back and forth, it's
OL,15,Fabsolutely soul-destroying.
OL,17,F"There just needs to be more support.
OL,18,FI feel so angry and emotional about
OL,19,Fit."
