OL,7,FA Neath Port Talbot Council
OL,8,Fspokesperson said it cannot comment on
OL,9,Findividual cases or on the waiting
OL,10,Flists of external services, but said
OL,11,Fthat they "understand" Betsan's
OL,12,Fconcerns.
OL,14,FA statement said: "We endeavour to
OL,15,Fensure the needs of children and young
OL,16,Fpeople with additional complex needs
OL,17,Fare met within a specialist provision.
