OL,5,Cchildcare
OL,7,F"The local authority continues to
OL,8,Foffer support to families whose
OL,9,Fchildren have additional needs to
OL,10,Fidentify suitable childcare and where
OL,11,Fappropriate, contribute to the cost of
OL,12,Fadditional support.
OL,14,F"Officers within the council have
OL,15,Fcontributed to the Senedd's report, we
OL,16,Frecognise the challenges faced by
OL,17,Ffamilies with complex additional needs
OL,18,Fand are committed to working with our
OL,19,Ffamilies to mitigate against these."
