OL,7,FMeanwhile, a Welsh Government
OL,8,Fspokesperson said it has invested more
OL,9,Fthan #107million into implementing of
OL,10,Four ALN reforms since 2020, and is
OL,11,Fcommitted to "breaking down barriers
OL,12,Ffor all learners".
OL,14,FIt added: "The Flying Start childcare
OL,15,Fexpansion has increased the numbers of
OL,16,Ftwo-year-olds who can access funded
OL,17,Fquality childcare, and created
OL,18,Fopportunities for children to be
OL,19,Fsupported with ALN before they start
OL,20,Fearly years education at three years
OL,21,Fold."
